<h1 id="isolation">Isolation</h1>

<p>Encapsulation is a subset of Isolation.</p>

<p>Isolation prevents <em>all</em> dependencies from leaking out.  Data must be passed via ports.</p>

<p>Encapsulation allowed <em>some</em> dependencies to leak out, e.g. control flow (In mehtod overriding).</p>

<p>[Example: C provided full isolation.]</p>

